---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Affiliate Disclosure — Trove Collections">
  <h1>Affiliate Disclosure</h1>

  <p class="lede">
    Trove Collections, LLC participates in affiliate marketing programs. Here is
    how that works, in plain English.
  </p>

  <h2>What this means</h2>
  <p>
    Many of the product links on this site are affiliate links. If you click one
    and buy something — whether the item we linked to or anything else from that
    retailer during your visit — we may earn a small commission. The price you
    pay is the same either way. You are not charged extra for buying through our
    link.
  </p>

  <h2>The rule we operate under</h2>
  <p>
    We only feature items that we — or someone in our trusted curator circle —
    have personally used and would give as a gift. Editorial integrity is the
    entire point of this site. We will never feature an item just because we
    could earn a commission from it. If a product is popular but no one in our
    circle has actually used it, it does not appear here.
  </p>

  <h2>Programs we participate in</h2>
  <p>
    We are part of, or in the application process with, the following affiliate
    networks and brand-direct programs (this list is updated as programs are
    approved): Amazon Associates, ShareASale, Awin, Rakuten Advertising, Commission
    Junction (CJ), Impact, plus brand-direct programs with Sephora, Ulta, UGG,
    Etsy, Adagio Teas, Korin, Novica, TirTir, and others. Where a link goes to a
    program we are not yet enrolled in, no commission is earned — we still link
    because the recommendation is real.
  </p>

  <h2>What we will not do</h2>
  <p>
    We will not write fake reviews. We will not stretch the truth about a product
    we have not actually used. We will not change a recommendation based on which
    program pays more. If a product is wrong for you, we will say so. If a curator
    in our circle switches away from a product, we update the entry.
  </p>

  <h2>FTC compliance</h2>
  <p>
    This site complies with the Federal Trade Commission's 16 CFR Part 255
    guidelines on endorsements and testimonials. The short affiliate disclosure
    that appears above the footer on every page is the clear, conspicuous
    disclosure required by those guidelines. This page is the long-form version.
  </p>

  <h2>Questions</h2>
  <p>
    Email us at <a href="mailto:hello@trovecollections.com">hello@trovecollections.com</a>.
    We answer every message — usually within a day or two unless one of us is on a
    long-haul flight.
  </p>

  <p class="muted" style="margin-top: 2rem;">
    <em>Last updated: May 2026. Trove Collections, LLC is a single-member LLC
    organized in the United States.</em>
  </p>
</Layout>

<style>
  .lede {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    max-width: 60ch;
  }
  p { max-width: 65ch; }
</style>
